# Saratovka, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Saratovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Tarbagataysky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 210 as of 2010. There is 1 street.
Geography
Saratovka is located 22&nbsp;km north of Tarbagatay (the district's administrative centre) by road. Selenga is the nearest rural locality.
